<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>222</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiin! Belampu Aw ka za'i,
 Gamlak thim leh lauhum nuoiah;
 Belampu huong sung apat mang,
 Belam chu hawlin, A sam hi.

[V2]
 Hun puiin, hun puiin!
 Gitloh mun apat hun puiin;
 Hun puiin, hun puiin!
 Vakmang Isu kawmah puiin.

[V3]
 2. Belampu pha panpih ding kuo?
 A vakmangte hawldawk pih ding;
 A huongah kuon hunpuilut ding?
 Lauhna apat bitna huongah?

[V4]
 3. Gamthip achun a Aw u chuh za'n,
 Tang gam mun sang leh lauhum ah;
 Ngaiin! Lalpau thugen chuh,
 &quot;Ka Belam mangte va hawlin!&quot;</lyrics>
<title>BRING THEM IN</title>
</song>